				<date>2010-02-03</date>
				<rev-version>0.3.4</rev-version>
				<changelog lang="en-gb">
					<change>Changed Points calculating according to new 2010 F1 rules (25-18-15-12-10-8-6-4-2-1)</change>
					<change>Changed Qualify design. We have now 26 drivers. In Q1 and Q2 eight driver will drop out</change>
					<change>BugFix: Module ACP Team/Driver language button.</change>
					<change>Added: Saison reset in ACP will remove driver and team penalty points.</change>
				</changelog>
				<changelog lang="de">
					<change>Punktberechnung an die neuen F1 Regeln von 2010 angepasst (25-18-15-12-10-8-6-4-2-1)</change>
